Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:02.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと好きでした
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.39,0:00:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I always have.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:06.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと好きでした
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.40,0:00:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,From the first time I saw you, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.48,0:00:09.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと始めてあった時から
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me a while to understand myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.54,0:00:12.63,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は 分からなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.73,0:00:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,but I fell in love too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:15.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.32,0:00:18.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きに なってた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was just a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:30.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ようするに あれか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.29,0:00:32.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,夢オチか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.81,0:00:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You already said that yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:34.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それ昨日も言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.00,0:00:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.11,0:00:36.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.36,0:00:38.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いくら夏だからって
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's summer, but you'll still catch a cold if you fall asleep out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.21,0:00:41.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんなところで寝てたら風邪引いちゃうわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:42.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.65,0:00:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:47.60,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これで安心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.13,0:00:52.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,夢 見てたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I had this dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.51,0:00:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:53.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どんな
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.12,0:00:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I dreamed that we got together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:57.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩と恋人同士になる夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:00.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,現実だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.36,0:01:04.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんか まだ信じられなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I still can't believe it{'s not butter}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Tanigawa to thank.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:07.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川さんのおかげ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,She helped me realize how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.19,0:01:12.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の気持ち 気づかせてくれたから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:18.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川 まだ 体調悪いのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if she's still feeling under the weather..
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:29.80,诸神-警示标语-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(629,16)}本字幕由诸神字幕组制作，仅供交流学习，禁止用于商业用途\N更多中日双语字幕，请登录www.kamigami.org
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:29.80,诸神-staff-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,日听：秋水无痕 翻译：yaya 校对：小草爱吃梨 Syura 时间轴：小青
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{part a}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks. My eyes are still puffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.01,0:01:26.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ひどい まだ腫れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.37,0:01:29.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんな顔じゃ 皆の前に出ていけない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.38,0:01:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let everyone see me like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.18,0:01:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it. It's no worse than usu—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:31.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,気にすることねえだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:32.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,たいして変わんっ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.40,0:01:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, did you tell everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.50,0:01:35.41,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それより 皆には連絡してくれたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.91,0:01:38.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とりあえず 夏風邪ってことにしておいた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.93,0:01:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I told them you have a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.57,0:01:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.59,0:01:39.96,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ 妥当よね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:42.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are friends for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.07,0:01:45.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ま 幼馴染だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.28,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ね 一昨日のことは
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,About the day before yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:52.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,誰にも言ってねえから 安心しろよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.60,0:01:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't told anyone, so don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm making lunch now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:01:59.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ねえ そろそろお昼にするけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.61,0:02:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want some, Tetsuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.62,0:02:01.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎君 食べていく
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be glad t—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:02.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ ありがとうございま
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro has something to do! He's going home soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.80,0:02:05.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎 用事あるって すぐ帰るから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.36,0:02:07.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうみたいです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love Kaito...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.47,0:02:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:22.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きなの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.54,0:02:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:27.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:29.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,えっ おい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.46,0:02:31.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.56,0:02:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:33.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はちょっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.10,0:02:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:34.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ついてくんな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.70,0:02:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:38.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今頃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:41.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あいつ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:45.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.14,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,北原さん だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Kitahara, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.26,0:03:01.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,同じ小学校だったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.32,0:03:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to elementary school together, but this is the first time we've been in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:04.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一緒のクラスになるのは初めてだね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.54,0:03:06.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川柑菜 これからよろしく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tanigawa Kanna. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:08.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん よろしく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.70,0:03:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same class again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:10.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また 同じクラスか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.98,0:03:12.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,代わり映えしねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.02,0:03:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't get rid of you, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.73,0:03:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You took the words right out of my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それはこっちのセリフです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. This is Ishigaki Tetsuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:17.12,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ 石垣哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We grew up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:18.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,幼馴染
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.58,0:03:20.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よろしく 北原美桜さん
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you, Kitahara Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.15,0:03:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私の 名前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.38,0:03:24.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれ 知り合い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just memorized all the girls' names and faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:28.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや 女子の顔と名前を全部記憶してきた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know whether to be impressed or think you're an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:30.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まめっていうか バカっていうか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just see I'm a gentleman who champions the cause of feminism?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:34.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,フェミニストのジェントルマンって解釈はできない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.{avi}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:34.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,できない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.34,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,時間 かかったんだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Memorizing them was so much effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,無駄な努力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Effort wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's been...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:44.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれから もう 三年
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}three years already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.03,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:48.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:49.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どっか行くの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜のお見舞いに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see how Kanna is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.53,0:03:54.29,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ やめたほうがいい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You probably shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:56.91,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いや 今あいつ目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Her eyes are— Cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,目が
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.34,0:03:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Her eyes are cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant she has a cold. She doesn't want to spread it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:01.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,風邪移すと嫌だからって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She wouldn't let me see her either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:02.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺も 断られたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You went there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:06.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜のとこ 行ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my friend, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.82,0:04:08.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,幼馴染だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お 美桜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お腹 空いてない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:18.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お見舞いのケーキ 無駄になっちゃうのなんだし
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.50,0:04:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I made her a cake, and I'd hate to see it go to waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.74,0:04:22.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごちそうさまでした
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.00,0:04:24.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい お粗末さまです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:31.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.05,0:04:35.00,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はあ フィルムの整理しようと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.22,0:04:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd get all my reels in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:38.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬先輩が山ほど撮ってきてくれるから
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemon shot a mile of footage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だいぶ 溜まって
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's been piling up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I need a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何かないとダメ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.62,0:04:53.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私ね くっついてるのが好きみたい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I like cuddling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you not like me like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:56.41,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君はこういうの嫌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:58.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,す そんなこと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I like it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:02.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺も 嫌いじゃないんです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:05.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,良かった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.68,0:05:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.72,0:05:17.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私のことは気にしないで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そのまま続けて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.27,0:05:20.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,気にします
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.56,0:05:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So you two are a couple now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:22.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,できたのね あなたたち
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:27.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ま まあ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.79,0:05:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:28.72,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう や
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:30.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああああ 何言い出すんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you implying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.05,0:05:31.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ドサクサに紛れて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,良かったわね イチカ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:36.36,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.51,0:05:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kirishima. I've got a gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:42.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,霧島君 これは私からの プレゼントよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,な 何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:47.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何がです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:48.92,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だって今
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She just gave you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Lemon!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.00,0:05:50.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,檸檬先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.54,0:05:51.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大切にするのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Treasure this miraculous joining of two souls well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この 奇跡のような出会いを
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:58.97,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごちそうさん
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.13,0:05:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.86,0:06:01.77,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ 食った 食った
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.28,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,やっぱ 美桜のケーキはうまいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.32,0:06:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Your cake was delicious, Mio.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing good about me otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:07.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私には これぐらいしか 取り柄がないから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.41,0:06:09.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あるだけ いいじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.42,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.98,0:06:11.72,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎君だってあるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have things going for you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.16,0:06:13.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,背が高くて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're tall, you're handsome, you're good with your hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:15.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ルックスがよくて
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,手先が器用で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're good at remembering the faces and names of girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,女の子の顔と名前を覚えるのが得意で
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno about that last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.49,0:06:21.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなの取り柄じゃないって
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to ask you something for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.97,0:06:25.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,聞きにくいこと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:26.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,聞いていいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:27.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you ask Takatsuki to be in the movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.44,0:06:32.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,映画作りにどうして 貴月先輩を誘ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.97,0:06:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it seemed like that's what Kai wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海が そうしてほしそうだったからだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:40.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まさか 先輩が引き受けるとは思わなかったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought she'd actually say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.97,0:06:42.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜の気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.02,0:06:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You knew about Kanna's feelings, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:43.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,知ってたよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.62,0:06:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been so close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.64,0:06:47.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あんなに近くにいるんだもん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:50.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私が分かったんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.40,0:06:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If I noticed, I'm sure you did too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:51.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,知らないわけないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you ask Takatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.20,0:06:55.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして 貴月先輩を誘ったの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.42,0:07:00.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩と霧島君が仲良くなったら
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:06:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want her and Kirishima to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.11,0:07:00.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違う
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.36,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Kanna would...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.42,0:07:02.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I said that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:03.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,違うって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to support Kai, so I asked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:08.41,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海を応援しようと思ったから 先輩に声をかけた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜が映画作りに参加すれば
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.98,0:07:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the movie would bring Kai and Kanna together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.39,0:07:13.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人との距離が縮められると思った
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:17.90,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それが どういう結果になるかなんて分かんねえけど
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.31,0:07:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know it would turn out like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.74,0:07:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to help both of them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.82,0:07:20.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺はどっちも応援しようとしたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:22.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.30,0:07:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So what about your own feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:28.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だったら 哲郎君の気持ちはどこに行くの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your feelings for Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜への気持ちは どこへ行くの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.96,0:07:36.74,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだよそれ お前 何言って
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.58,0:07:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know because I've been watching you this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.84,0:07:38.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと見てきたから 分かるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You've only had eyes for Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:42.23,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎君はずっと柑菜のことだけ見てたから
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:43.25,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうなんじゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you lying to yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうして 自分にウソをつくの
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to resolve itself if you keep avoiding the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:51.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうやって はぐらかし続けても
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,時間が解決してくれるわけじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me to just say what I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,言いたいこと言えよって
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.27,0:07:59.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私にそう言ったの哲郎君でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I tried to be brave for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:02.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 私は勇気を振り絞ったのに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.24,0:08:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:04.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好き
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:10.54,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎君が 好き
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大好き
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの時は返事はいいって言ったけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I didn't need an answer back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:19.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,聞かせてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but will you tell me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.38,0:08:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Mio... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,美桜 俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.61,0:08:27.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前のこと その
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't dislike you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.60,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,嫌いじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:31.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも 俺 今は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.48,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.63,0:08:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰るね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll just act like nothing's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,普通でいるんだ 私
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.31,0:08:44.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,夏休み 楽しく皆で映画を撮るの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.36,0:08:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all gonna have fun filming the movie over summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.11,0:08:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make the movie and show it at the school fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:48.60,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,映画を作って 学園祭なんかで発表して
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll just continue being the usual Tanigawa Kanna.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,とにかく いつもの谷川柑菜でいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そう決めたの
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:55.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜な
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.09,0:08:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanna...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:57.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanigawa? She was here toda—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:58.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川なら 今日 うちに
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:09:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She loves you, Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あいつ 海が好きだぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:02.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I love him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:04.55,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君が
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:10.29,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうしようってんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What {\i1}can{\i0} I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:14.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何が できるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.77,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(772,384)\fs70\blur0.55}Yours and Ours
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.77,ep title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(782,179)\blur0.55}Episode Ten
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.94,0:09:25.27,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いてえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.02,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{part b}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.36,0:09:29.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.04,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.37,0:09:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.43,0:09:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go take a walk to cool off a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:35.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,良かったら 湯冷ましがったら 散歩にでもいきません
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.12,0:09:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.56,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん いいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.22,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうね せっかくだから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:41.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,りのん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.29,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おう すげえ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.49,0:09:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.59,0:09:46.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:48.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,夜も素敵だろうなって
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.90,0:09:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured the view would be great at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.43,0:09:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's such an important place for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.54,0:09:52.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その 思い出の場所だし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こんなにも自然が残ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so unspoiled by civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.53,0:09:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.47,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,おかしいな 初めて来た星なのに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my first time coming to this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's like I can remember seeing all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんだか 懐かしい感じがする
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Ichika...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.35,0:10:06.12,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのう 先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let me help you look around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.33,0:10:08.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,改めて 俺にも
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:13.12,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,その 場所探し 手伝わせてもらえませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:16.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺 少しでも 先輩の
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:16.63,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.04,0:10:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:18.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.04,0:10:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:20.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.08,0:10:22.48,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも もういいの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, that's why I originally came to this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:27.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,確かに 私は それが目的でこの星に来たわ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.28,0:10:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but it was really just an excuse to start traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.29,0:10:31.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,というより この旅をきっかけにしたかったの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.19,0:10:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't really have a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:34.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,別に 何があったわけじゃないの
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから 何かしたいと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought I wanted to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.56,0:10:41.65,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺もです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:47.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺も これで何かを始めたいと思ったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to start something using this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought, "If I could create something..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:49.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何か出来ればって
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そっか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.10,0:10:53.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,同じだったんですね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.14,0:10:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess we're the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.34,0:10:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me want to help grant your wish even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:58.16,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なら 余計俺は先輩の願いを叶えてあげたい
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I want to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:02.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,今 私は海人君といたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.46,0:11:07.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a movie with you and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:07.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君と 皆と 一緒に映画を撮りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my wish now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:10.09,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それが 今の私の願いなの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.18,0:11:12.43,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.89,0:11:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I already knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かっていたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:22.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,この世界に永遠は存在しないって
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.43,0:11:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nothing in this world lasts forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.88,0:11:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can you not tell him because you're an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙人だから ダメって言うんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.13,0:11:30.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつまでも一緒にいられないから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.21,0:11:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can't be with him because you can't stay here forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.97,0:11:33.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君の気持ちに答えられないっていうんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to use that as an excuse to keep running away from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういうの言い訳にして
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君から ずっと逃げ続ける気ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あれで良かったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.21,0:11:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I did the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君の思いが叶うんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,それで いいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:53.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょっと何なのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't said anything since you got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.33,0:11:56.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,帰ってきてから ずっと黙りでさ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:58.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,なんかあったの
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:11:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.63,0:11:59.62,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,姉ちゃんに相談してみ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.60,0:12:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that's your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:04.84,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,言っとくけど あんたの悪い部分はそこよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing's going to fix itself if you keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:08.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,黙ってたって物事は解決しないのよね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.07,0:12:10.76,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,格好つけても無駄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just keep acting cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You might look like you've got things under control,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.29,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そつなく生きてるように見えても
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.57,0:12:15.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あたしから見りゃただのガキだっての
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,but I know you're just a kid at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You're here because you left your husband. You have no room to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:19.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,出戻りが偉そうに人生語ってんじゃねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't leave him. I just ran away for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:22.06,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,出戻りじゃなくて 家出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, I still have a home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:24.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つまり 帰る場所があるってこと
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A fight between wife and husband can take many forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.67,0:12:28.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,夫婦喧嘩の種類にもいろいろあんのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But you haven't even gone out with a girl, so I don't think you'd understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:31.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ま 女の子と付き合ったこともないあんたには
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分からないだろうけど
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, it reeks of virgin in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.46,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ いやだいやだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:37.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ここ 童貞の匂いがするわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だったら かえ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.15,0:12:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then get the hell—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:40.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,来た来た
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the room, Tetsuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:42.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,世話になったね 哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.17,0:12:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ま 頑張んな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.14,0:12:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.23,0:12:46.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう 遅い
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:49.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まちくたびれた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.67,0:12:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to wait so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:52.57,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,また このオチかの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so she just leaves again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:58.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい もしもし
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.86,0:12:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tetsuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.03,0:12:59.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, Kai?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.13,0:13:01.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,どうした 海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to start filming again the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.41,0:13:04.87,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,明後日から 撮影再開しようと思って
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That okay with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.46,0:13:06.03,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.56,0:13:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine with me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:08.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいけど でも
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:13.30,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(412,322)\c&H1F261E&\blur1\fs58\fax0.23\fnPixel Arial 11\frz9.314\b1}Kirishima Kaito
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:13.30,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,161)\c&H242922&\blur1\fs48\fax0.23\fnPixel Arial 11\b1\frz8.716}Calling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ichika will be there too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.67,0:13:10.83,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,先輩も ちゃんと来てくれるからさ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:13.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あ そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.27,0:13:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So did you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.34,0:13:16.62,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前 もしかして先輩と
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:20.95,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ それは 皆と会ったときにちゃんと話すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.97,0:13:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, I'll tell everyone in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.62,0:13:22.94,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃあ やっぱり
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pretty much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん まあ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.72,0:13:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:33.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,じゃ 柑菜はどうするんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what about Kanna?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:38.20,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(412,322)\c&H1F261E&\blur1\fs58\fax0.23\fnPixel Arial 11\frz9.314\b1}Kirishima Kaito
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:38.20,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(355,161)\c&H242922&\blur1\fs48\fax0.23\fnPixel Arial 11\b1\frz8.716}Calling
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:37.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから なおさら ちゃんと言わなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's why I need to talk to everyone and tell them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.35,0:13:39.07,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺の気持ちを
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tetsuro, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:45.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎 俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:47.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tetsuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.79,0:13:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:55.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何やってんだ 俺は
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.09,0:13:55.80,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(367,601)\blur0.6\fax0.15\fs25\fnTabitha\b1\c&H31332D&\frz15.693}Filming on Okinawa
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.02,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん よし
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.14,0:14:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll be fine for tomorrow's shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.24,0:14:02.98,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,これなら 明日からの撮影も大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:05.78,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫 うん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.09,0:14:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:06.80,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.36,0:14:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Call for you, Kanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:09.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜 電話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.99,signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(611,650)\blur0.65\fax0.15\fs40\fnTabitha\b1\c&H31332D&}Filming on Okinawa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.44,0:14:11.35,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you call me out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.13,0:14:17.54,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何よ こんなところに呼び出して
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to be getting over a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:20.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,一応病み上がりってことになってるんだから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.14,0:14:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares? You're not all swollen up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:23.67,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いいじゃんか 腫れも収まってるし
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:25.42,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,まあ ね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.83,0:14:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:27.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,よっしゃ マジック
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang it, you got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.78,0:14:28.85,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ああ やられた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We came here a lot when we were in kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.02,0:14:31.30,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,幼稚園のごろ よく来たよな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.32,0:14:33.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I was taller than you back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.92,0:14:37.15,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,あのごろ 私のほうが背が高かったのにな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.51,0:14:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Now look how much taller you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.82,0:14:40.41,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつの間にか こんなに差を付けられてさ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.87,0:14:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And you always saved me from getting bullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:43.81,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いじめられてた 俺を よく助けてくれてたよな
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:47.17,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,柑菜パンチは無敵だったもん
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Beware the fearsome Kanna Punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.35,0:14:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You were pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.32,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,格好良かったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you acting so creepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:53.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何よ 気味悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.61,0:14:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't just call me out here to talk about the past, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:57.18,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で 昔話するために 呼び出したわけじゃないんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened to your foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.40,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,っていうか 何その足
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:01.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ちょ ちょっとな
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So what did you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,で 要件は何なの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:08.64,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うん その
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to say something about Kaito, don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:14.48,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君のことなら 言わなくていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:17.31,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何となくわかるから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:19.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は 大丈夫だから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.44,0:15:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't need anything else, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,他に用がないなら 帰るね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought everything would be fine if things worked out between you and Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:33.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前と海がうまく行けばいいと思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:36.11,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,でも そんなの見たくなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't want to see that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that if Kai and Ichika hit it off, you'd be open to whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:39.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海と先輩がうまく行けば
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.70,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前がフリーになるとか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But that would never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.54,0:15:44.08,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,つまんねえ期待してさ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stupid of me to think it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:46.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そんなこと あるわけねえのに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:49.68,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I played with the heart of the girl I like, only to make her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:54.05,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きな女の子 振り回して挙句泣かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And now I can't do anything about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.39,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何もできねえで
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.68,0:16:00.21,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きな人って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:04.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,う ウソでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.76,0:16:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.82,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,本気
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.94,0:16:09.71,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いつから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.75,0:16:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.78,0:16:11.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと前から
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:18.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう 頭ん中 くしゃくしゃになってるときに
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind's already a mess,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and now you drop this on me too? You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:21.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,いきなり何言い出すのよ バカ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the timing's really bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:24.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ホント タイミング悪いよな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.35,0:16:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm glad to finally get it off my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.47,0:16:28.10,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,けど ようやく言えた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:30.93,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,哲郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Tetsuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.45,0:16:35.26,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,分かってる お前は 海のことが好きだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like Kai, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Kai likes Ichika, but that doesn't change anything, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.87,0:16:38.52,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海がイチカ先輩を好きでも
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:39.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そうだよな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's what I liked about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.94,0:16:43.44,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,そういうお前が好きだった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.25,0:16:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you get to say all that stuff and look so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:46.37,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,何よ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,自分だけ言いたいこと言って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.62,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,満足したような顔して
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,When I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:51.88,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:55.19,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:00.58,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,我慢すんな 柑菜は柑菜のままでいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to hold it all in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.66,0:17:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just be yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:07.20,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お 女の子の髪を軽々しく触るな
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch a girl's hair like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.37,0:17:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I already know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:09.13,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,言われなくても分かってる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:11.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cry, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,泣いていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:27.99,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,泣かねえよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:30.63,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,意地っ張り
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:32.38,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,うるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, should you even be here to see this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.29,0:17:37.24,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,っていうかさ お前ここに来るのは犯則だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.26,0:17:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls are tenacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,女の子は強かなんです
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.54,0:17:42.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,お前 強いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do a lot when you're in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.56,0:17:46.49,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,好きな人ができるよ 強くなれるんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I was able to change because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:50.27,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私は 哲郎君のお陰で変われたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.77,0:17:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can at least think about changing, about being stronger, because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:53.89,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ううん 少なくとも 変わろうって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.59,0:17:56.01,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,強くなろうって
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:57.79,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,思えるようになった
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.16,0:18:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.86,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,だから ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.61,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,こっちのセルフだって
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll... do it...
