Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.12,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.12,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanigawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your cold better?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:47.53,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,もう 風邪いいのか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You want some watermelon?
