Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.75,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaito, I like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:01.50,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,私
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:03.51,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,海人君が好き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.77,0:19:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've liked you for a long time now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.82,0:19:05.45,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ずっと前から 好きだった
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:07.69,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,大好き
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry, Tanigawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:11.59,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,ごめん 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I love Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:14.97,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,俺は 先輩が好きだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:16.96,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.73,盛夏-JP-ja,NTP,0,0,0,,聞いてくれて ありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.12,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for hearing me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make the best movie ever!
